## Introduction

This test suite is for testing sampleapp-android-tests specification

## Precondition

1. The node.js and Android SDK must be functional
2. Install nodeunit: sudo npm install nodeunit -g
3. Download crosswalk-app-tools to apptools-sampleapp-tests/tools, then install npm
  3.1 cd tools, then download source code from https://github.com/crosswalk-project/crosswalk-app-tools
  3.2 Run commands: cd crosswalk-app-tools, then run: npm install
4. Connect Android devices to your localhost
5. The main script is crosswalk-app-tools/src/crosswalk-app. Set environment PATH or invoke with directory
6. Environment variable configuration:
  6.1 export ANDROID_HOME=$(dirname $(dirname $(which android)))
  6.2 export CROSSWALK_APP_TOOLS_CACHE_DIR=/path/to/opt/apptools-sampleapp-tests/tools

